snippet: Anna Pogorilaya, a 15-year-old from Russia competing in her first senior Grand Prix, hit seven triple jumps to win the Cup of China in Beijing.
abstract: Russian figure skater Anna Pogorilaya, competing in her first senior Grand Prix, hits seven triple jumps to win the Cup of China in Beijing.
lead_paragraph: Anna Pogorilaya, a 15-year-old from Russia competing in her first senior Grand Prix, hit seven triple jumps to win the Cup of China in Beijing.

headline.main: Russian Teenager Wins Cup of China
